title: Gingerfeet - High and Above : The First Wave [2013]
description:
Gingerfeet is considered as India's Answer to Funk Alternative Rock. The band released their debut record - High and Above : The First Wave in September 2013 which has bagged great International acclaim from various magazines like- Rollingstone Magazine,AATR[UK],GRTR[UK], RIP Magazines and also from various icons of the music industry namely - Lonn Friend [Editor - RIP Magazines], Robert M Knight [Rock Prophecies] and Ron Bumblefoot Thal [Guns n Roses]


High and Above: The First Wave Track list:

1. Fake You
2. No Division
3. God Forbid
4. Am I dreaming or what?
5. Stars
6. High and Above
7. Mr. Boombastic
8. The Vibe
9. Game On #


High and Above is produced by Rhitabrata Kar [RBK Studio-Kolkata,India]
# Produced by Suvam Moitra.
